title: 775. Senior Bowl Day 2 Practice Standouts + Quarterbacks Breakdown
itunes:title: 775. Senior Bowl Day 2 Practice Standouts + Quarterbacks Breakdown
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Lance Zierlein are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, DJ and Lance give their standout players from the second day of Senior Bowl practice. Then, the duo break down the quarterbacks' performances from practice. Next, Lance goes through more of his standout players. To wrap up the show, Lance gives a funny impersonation of a former NFL quarterback to hype up the Senior Bowl participants.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
